{"tid":2348810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子西貢車內燒炭亡 車尾遺Happy New Year字句","createTime":"2021-01-01T05:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T00:38:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":175,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"3fefb64909461142ed7c1579b2784469e73e3fac","tid":2348810,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"一名中年男子早上被發現，在泊於西貢大網仔路近早禾坑村巴士站附近的私家車內燒炭死亡。私家車的車尾箱頂，被人寫上「Happy New Year」（新年快樂）字句。<br />\n<br />\n警方早上7時30分接獲途人報案，指現場一輛Tesla電動車內，有一名男子昏迷倒臥在拉平的司機位座椅上。消防到場後打開無上鎖的車門，事主昏迷由救護車送威爾斯親王醫院搶救後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警員在車廂後座位置發現一盆燒過的炭，正調查事件。而肇事Tesla布滿塵埃的車尾箱頂，被人寫上「Happy New Year」字句。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline .com/news/realtime/hk/1964979</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e05df32dd4daeb30335b4b3d5a674a4a2790a7d4","tid":2348810,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3182dac4d677bcc6942b7f7fc7640b607e62279","tid":2348810,"uid":810,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:10:09.000Z","msg":"Happy new year 2020 season2<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb734f11565450e04f99167fd2f7fa9547b00411","tid":2348810,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"香港已死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485e9b996d0f04e3c82939af9bec60eae268649e","tid":2348810,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a197ef7f303e3aad81cd953b10bcfa5ca64001","tid":2348810,"uid":214502,"like":63,"disli